Class BTOExercise

java.lang.Object
sg.edu.ntu.sc2002.ay2425.fcsdGroup2.model.entities.BTOExercise
public class BTOExercise extends Object
Represents a BTO Exercise that groups multiple BTO Projects together. Tracks exercise name, status, total applicants, and associated projects.
